  "texts": [
    "Many database tasks require low latency.",
    "However, there are three factors that can increase the interaction latency and cost with LLM.",
    "(i) It can be time-consuming to actively generate prompt for input (e.g., retrieving suitable examples from candidate ones).",
    "(ii) Long prompts often include more useful information for LLM, but can take longer processing time for LLM.",
    "(iii) Some complex tasks can be better solved by calling LLM for several rounds and interactively adjusting the prompt."
  ],
